{"about_the_game":"Drift Experience Japan is a small, experience oriented game.<br>Experience modern Assets developed by gifted creators using the unreal Engine 5.<br>Drift Experience Japan: Supporter Edition gives you extra content to your game and a Bonus Mode.<br>Experience the roads around Haruna, Hakone, Gunma, a garage, a practice- and a race track.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tracks</h2>Choose between the tracks and select day and at night settings.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322410/extras/drift_tracks_supporter_edition.png?t=1738360031\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Drift</h2>The car has an challenging arcade drift handling and can be controlled by keyboard or gamepad.<br>It may take some to time to get used to it.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322410/extras/drift_gameplay_supporter_Edition.png?t=1738360031\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customization</h2>Fully customize your car. Change tires, different body parts, paint.<br>Customization is available in Gunma, Haruna, garage and on practice track. Use a prebuild setup in Hakone and on the race track with modified setups!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322410/extras/CUSTOM_drift.png?t=1738360031\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Bonus</h2>Bonus RC Stunt Mode: Try to collect all stars!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322410/extras/bonus_mode_supporter_edition.png?t=1738360031\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 circuits<br></li><li>day / night settings for 4 circuits<br></li><li>car customizing in 3 circuits (Haruna, Gunma, Practice)<br></li><li>challenging arcade drift physics <br></li><li>RC Bonus</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322410/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738360031","background_raw":"https://s